sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as UI
    participant SR as support_routes.py
    participant EH as entry_handler.py
    participant RH as reasoning_handler.py
    participant G as graph
    participant IC as intent_class_node
    participant LLM as Azure OpenAI
    participant RF as response_formatter

    User->>UI: ambiguous question
    UI->>SR: POST /entry/reasoning
    Note over SR: handle_reasoning_entry() L108
    SR->>SR: _dispatch_entry_handler() L82
    SR->>EH: handle_entry(envelope) L84
    EH->>RH: handle_ai_reasoning() L68
    RH->>G: graph.invoke(initial_state) L66
    Note over G: start_node -> context_node

    G->>IC: intent_classification_node(state) L11
    Note over IC: get_llm("intent", 0.0)
    IC->>LLM: llm.with_structured_output(_RawClass)
    LLM-->>IC: intent, confidence=0.25
    Note over IC: coerce_raw() -> low_confidence=True
    IC-->>G: classification_low_confidence=True

    Note over G: question_readiness -> router
    Note over G: domain node -> response_formatter
    G->>RF: response_formatter_node(state) L9
    RF-->>G: final_response

    G-->>RH: graph_result
    Note over RH: classification_low_confidence==True L71
    RH->>RH: build_clarifying_response() L75
    Note over RH: status=accepted L109
    Note over RH: summary=_CLARIFYING_TEXT L102
    Note over RH: suggestions=_CLARIFYING_SUGGESTIONS L104
    RH-->>SR: EntryResponseEnvelope status=accepted

    SR-->>UI: EntryResponseEnvelope
    UI-->>User: clarifying message + 4 suggestion chips
